{"title_page": "Plan Panni Pannanum", "text_new": "[[File:Plan Panni Pannanum.jpg|thumb|Plan Panni Pannanum Poster]]\nPlan Panni Pannanum is an upcoming 2020 Indian Tamil-language Comedy film directedby \u00a0Badri Venkatesh , produced by Rajesh Kumar &amp;amp; Sinthan L from Positive Print Studios. The story is written by G.Radhakrishnan, dialogues by A.C Karnamoorthy. The film stars Rio Raj and \u00a0Ramya Nambessan \u00a0playing the lead roles. The music for the film is composed by \u00a0Yuvan Shankar Raja \u00a0while Cinematography is handled by \u00a0Rajasekar \u00a0and editing is done by Sam. The film is set to be released in the last week of April.\n\n=== Cast ===\n\n* [[Rio Raj]]<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n* [[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n* [[Santhana Bharathi]]\n* [[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n* [[Bala Saravanan]]\n* Thangadurai\n* [[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n* Poornima Ravi\n\n=== Music ===\nThe music and score is composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]. The audio rights have been acquired by [[Sony Music India]]. The lyrics for the songs are written by [[Arunraja Kamaraj]] and Niranjan Bharathi.\n\nThe first single track, \"Ennodu Vaa\" was released on 27th February 2020. The song, was released live on [[Sun Music|sun music]] \u00a0and was uploaded on [[YouTube (channel)|Youtube]] at the same time.\n\nThe audio launch happened on 11th March 2020 at [[Sathyam cinemas|Sathyam Cinemas]].\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|'''No.'''\n|'''Title'''\n|'''Lyrics'''\n|'''Singer(s)'''\n|-\n|1.\n|Plan Panni\n|[[Premgi Amaren]]\n|[[Arunraja Kamaraj]]\n|-\n|2.\n|Allola Kallolam\n|[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|3.\n|Kanave Urave\n|[[Shreya Ghoshal]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|4.\n|Ennodu Vaa\n|[[Rajaganapathy|Raja Ganapathy]] , [[Ramya NSK]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|5.\n|Neengum Bothail\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|}\n\n=== Promotion and Release ===\nThe film's title was unveiled on 11th January 2020 which was released by [[Sivakarthikeyan]] and [[Vijay Sethupathi]]. The first look of the motion poster happened on 17th January 2020. The teaser was released on 21st February 2020 by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]].\n\n=== '''References''' ===\n\n# <nowiki>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/newTimes</nowiki> of india\n# <nowiki>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movie-details/plan-panni-pannanum/movieshow/73225412.cms</nowiki> <span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\u00a0Times of india\n# <nowiki>https://nettv4u.com/latest-tamil-celebrity-news/sivakarthikeyan-to-release-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look</nowiki> 16th January 2020\n# <nowiki>https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/vijay-sethupathi-and-sivakarthikeyan-releases-rio-raj-remya-nambeesan-yuvan-s-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look-motion-poster.html</nowiki><span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n# <nowiki>https://www.newsbugz.com/plan-panni-pannanum-tamil-movie/</nowiki> 22nd february 2020\n# <nowiki>http://view7media.com/tag/plan-panni-pannanum-audio-launch/</nowiki> 13th march 2020\n# <nowiki>https://thandoratimes.com/gallery-Plan-Pani-Pannanum-Audio-Launch857-1</nowiki><span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n# <nowiki>https://tamil.filmibeat.com/videos/i-said-only-one-joke-robo-shankar-plan-panni-pannanum-audio-launch-filmibeat-tamil-106660.html</nowiki><span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n# <nowiki>https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/jan/12/rio-rajs-film-with-badri-titled-plan-panni-pannanum-16494.html</nowiki><span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n# <nowiki>https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/jan/27/ramya-nambeesan-sings-for-yuvan-shankar-raja-in-plan-panni-pannanum-16724.html</nowi