]] Competition Modern Champion<ref name=TargaWest2010CMM>{{cite web |url=http://www.targawest.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/CMM10_RESULTSFORLEG_QUITTARGAWEST.pdf |title=Quit Targa West 2010 \u2013 Competition Modern \u2013 Final |publisher=TargaWest |location=Australia |access-date=February 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2010||''[[Yahoo]]'' \u2013 Listed as having one of the best resale values of any sports car.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://autos.yahoo.com/articles/autos_content_landing_pages/1487/sports-cars-with-the-best-resale-value/|title=Sports cars with best resale value&#124; Yahoo Autos |publisher=Yahoo.com |accessdate=July 30, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|2011||[[Targa Tasmania]] Modern Champion\n|-\n|2011||[[Targa West]] Competition Modern Champion<ref name=TargaWest2011CMM>{{cite web |url=http://www.rallyresults.com.au/targawest/2011/Comp_Modern_Final.pdf |title=Quit Targa West 2011 \u2013 Final Classifications \u2013 Competition Category \u2010 Modern|publisher=TargaWest |location=Australia |access-date=February 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2011||Motor Magazine Performance Car Cup Winner<ref>[http://motoring.ninemsn.com.au/cars/features/8385982/performance-car-cup-2011-winner-nissan-gt-r Performance Car Cup 2011 Winner! Nissan GT-R]. Motoring.ninemsn.com.au (2011-12-08).</ref>\n|-\n|2013||[[Targa Adelaide]] \u2013 Modern Champion\n|}\n\n==Sales==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:right;\"\n! Calendar<br />Year\n! US !! Canada !! Japan !! Europe<br />(incl. UK)\n|-\n| 2007\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 807<ref name=SalesJapan>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.2009gtr.com/2012/03/japanese-market-nissan-gt-r-sales.html |title=Japanese Market Nissan GT-R Sales |author= |date=March 2012 |number=103 |magazine=GT-R Magazine |accessdate=February 8, 2018}}</ref> || \u2014\n|-\n| 2008\n| 1730<ref name=SalesGCBC/> || 137<ref name=SalesGCBC/> || 4871<ref name=SalesJapan /> || 1<ref name=SalesEurope>{{cite web |url=http://carsalesbase.com/european-car-sales-data/nissan/nissan-gtr/ |title=Nis